<h4 id="associate-instructor--department-of-intelligent-systems-engineering-indiana-university--bloomington-in-aug-2018---present">Associate Instructor | Department of Intelligent Systems Engineering, Indiana University – Bloomington, IN	Aug 2018 - Present</h4>
