      <li>Introduced FPGA development using verilog in Vivado focussed on hardware acceleration of software-based applications</li>
      <li>Tutored a hardware/software co-design based project for accelerating Machine Learning reducing clock cycles for dot products from 2210 cycles  to 130 cycles</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
